---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<section class="bg-white py-20">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12">Gracias por su confianza</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      
      <!-- Testimonio 1 -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center">
        <Icon name="mdi:account-edit" class="h-10 w-10 text-orange-500 mb-4" />
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">
          “Contraté el servicio de diseño web y fue un servicio rápido y siempre estuvieron pendientes.”
        </p>
        <img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="Elizabeth Hernández" class="h-20 w-20 rounded-full object-cover mb-2" />
        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Elizabeth Hernández</p>
        <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-2">Cliente</span>
        <div class="flex gap-1">
          <Icon name="mdi:star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
          <Icon name="mdi:star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
          <Icon name="mdi:star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
          <Icon name="mdi:star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
          <Icon name="mdi:star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonio 2 -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center">
        <Icon name="mdi:domain" class="h-10 w-10 text-blue-600 mb-4" />
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">
          “Nuestra empresa siempre en línea, con nuestra página web hemos incrementado nuestros clientes.”
        </p>
        <img src="/images/avatar3.png" alt="Construcciones" class="h-20 w-20 rounded-full object-cover mb-2" />
        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Construcciones</p>
        <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-2">Cliente</span>
        <div class="flex gap-1">
          <Icon name="mdi:star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
          <Icon name="mdi:star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
          <Icon name="mdi:star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
          <Icon name="mdi:star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
          <Icon name="mdi:star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonio 3 -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center">
        <Icon name="mdi:school" class="h-10 w-10 text-purple-600 mb-4" />
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">
          “Ahora tenemos más alumnos por ofrecer nuestros cursos en línea, indispensable tener un sitio web.”
        </p>
        <img src="/images/avatar1.png" alt="Cursos Online" class="h-20 w-20 rounded-full object-cover mb-2" />
        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Cursos Online</p>
        <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-2">Cliente</span>
        <div class="flex gap-1">
          <Icon name="mdi:star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
          <Icon name="mdi:star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
          <Icon name="mdi:star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
          <Icon name="mdi:star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
          <Icon name="mdi:star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonio 4 -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center">
        <Icon name="mdi:shopping" class="h-10 w-10 text-green-600 mb-4" />
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">
          “Recomiendo el diseño de tienda en línea, aumentaron mis ventas, ya que está disponible las 24 horas.”
        </p>
        <img src="/images/avatar2.png" alt="Ropa de Moda" class="h-20 w-20 rounded-full object-cover mb-2" />
        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Ropa de Moda</p>
        <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-2">Cliente</span>
        <div class="flex gap-1">
          <Icon name="mdi:star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
          <Icon name="mdi:star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
          <Icon name="mdi:star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
          <Icon name="mdi:star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
          <Icon name="mdi:star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>